UNITED STATES of America, Appellant, v. Edythe HOOPS, as Administratrix of the Estate of Fay E. Hoops, Deceased, et al., Appellees. No. 6628. Circuit Court of Appeals, Niiith Circuit. Oct. 12, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and JAMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
